trans-unit.source: Provides design-time support for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ScriptManagerProxy"></xref> control in a visual designer.
trans-unit.target: 에 대 한 디자인 타임 지원을 제공는 <xref href="System.Web.UI.ScriptManagerProxy"> </xref> 비주얼 디자이너에서 제어 합니다.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner> class documentation.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.ScriptManagerProxyDesigner"></xref> class.

The [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/add/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)] internally constructs a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ScriptManagerProxyDesigner> class when it creates the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManagerProxy> control or a copy of that control on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/add/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)] 의 새 인스턴스를 내부적으로 생성 된 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ScriptManagerProxyDesigner>클래스에서는 연결 된 <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManagerProxy>컨트롤 또는 디자인 화면에서 해당 컨트롤의 복사본입니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManagerProxy> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ScriptManagerProxyDesigner>

trans-unit.source: Returns the HTML markup that represents the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ScriptManagerProxy"></xref> control at design time.
trans-unit.target: HTML 태그를 반환 나타내는 <xref href="System.Web.UI.ScriptManagerProxy"> </xref> 디자인 타임에 컨트롤입니다.

trans-unit.source: Override this method to change the generated HTML of the <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManagerProxy> control at design time.
trans-unit.target: 생성된 된 HTML을 변경 하려면이 메서드를 재정의 하는 <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManagerProxy>디자인 타임에 컨트롤.</xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManagerProxy>

trans-unit.source: A string that contains the markup that is used to render the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ScriptManagerProxy"></xref> at design time.
trans-unit.target: 렌더링 하는 데 사용 되는 태그를 포함 하는 문자열은 <xref href="System.Web.UI.ScriptManagerProxy"> </xref> 디자인 타임에 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.ScriptManagerProxy"></xref> component that implements the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.IComponent"></xref> interface.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.ScriptManagerProxy"> </xref> 구현 하는 구성 요소는 <xref href="System.ComponentModel.IComponent"> </xref> 인터페이스입니다.
